{{!--
/**
 * Empty State Component Template
 *
 * PURPOSE:
 * Reusable component for displaying empty state messages when no data is available
 * or no results match current filters. Provides consistent user feedback across
 * the application for empty collections, failed searches, or uninitialized states.
 * Supports both custom messages and default fallback text.
 *
 * CONTEXT REQUIREMENTS:
 * @param {string} [message] - Optional custom message to display (falls back to default)
 *
 * ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:
 * - Status role for screen reader announcement of state changes
 * - Semantic paragraph structure for message content
 * - Consistent styling context for empty state recognition
 *
 * CUSTOMIZATION POINTS:
 * - Message content adaptable through context parameter
 * - Default fallback message provides consistent experience
 * - Styling controlled through CSS class targeting
 *
 * INTEGRATION:
 * - Used across multiple templates for consistent empty state display
 * - Supports spell lists, search results, and data collections
 * - Integrates with filtering and search systems
 * - Provides user feedback for application state changes
 */
--}}

<div class="empty-state" role="status">
	<p>{{#if message}}{{message}}{{else}}{{localize 'SPELLBOOK.UI.NoResults'}}{{/if}}</p>
</div>
